These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pear
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, d&b
1. the fan soul is on the far left##1
2. the fan d&b is not the person eating pear##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pear   | nectarine  |
| Sport   | soul | d&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, salsa
2 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the goat is not the fan salsa##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | rock | salsa      |
| Pet    | goat  | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, techno
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, sailing
1. the fan techno is on the left of the fan folk##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is not the fan folk##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | techno  | folk    |
| Sport   | handball | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, tram
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster
1. the person driving the tram is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | helicopter  | tram |
| Pet    | goldfish | hamster    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
City: san-francisco, london
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse
1. the person traveling to london is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
2. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | san-francisco  | london |
| Sport         | lacrosse | golf      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, dressmaker
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, polish
1. the musician is on the far right##1
2. the dressmaker is not the japanese##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | dressmaker  | musician      |
| Nationality   | polish | japanese |

